[{"id": 368, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-paladin\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Interpose</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You put yourself between them.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When an ally within reach would take a hit, spend <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> dice equal to the incoming hit \u2014 you become the target and the <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> absorbs it.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> The ally also gains <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Paladin</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 369, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-paladin\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Lay on Hands</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Not this one. Not today.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Medicine</strong> check. On success, touch an ally \u2014 they remove the worst thing pressing on them and recover a lost <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> They recover one additional lost <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Paladin</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 370, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Taunt</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You make yourself the problem they can't ignore.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Presence</strong> check. On success, draw an enemy's focus entirely to you \u2014 they are <strong>Rattled</strong> and must engage you before acting on anyone else.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> All enemies who hear it are <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 371, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-paladin\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Shield of Faith</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Belief, made solid.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Faith</strong> check. On success, grant <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> to yourself and one ally \u2014 the GM rolls a d6 for each. Those dice sit in front of their <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Dice</span> as protection.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Grant <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> to a third ally also.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Paladin</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 372, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-paladin\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Condition</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Aura of Protection</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">While in hand: you are a wall between them and harm.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">While this card is in hand, any ally adjacent to you may use your <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> dice as if they were their own. You are aware of every threat directed at them.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Gain one additional <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> die when this card is drawn.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Paladin</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 373, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-paladin\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Smite</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Conviction lands harder than steel.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Faith</strong> check. On success, <strong>Strike</strong> with divine force \u2014 the target is <strong>Exposed</strong> and you gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on the damage roll.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> The target is also <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Paladin</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 374, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-paladin\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Lay on Hands</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Not a miracle. A decision.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Faith</strong> check. On success, restore one ally's <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> \u2014 they recover a spent <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span> at its current face value.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> They also remove one negative condition.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Paladin</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 375, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-paladin\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Condition</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Oath of Vengeance</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">While in hand: you have named the debt.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">While this card is in hand, name one target. You have <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on all <strong>Actions</strong> against that target, and allies who Strike them gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on that Strike.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> The target is <strong>Exposed</strong> to all attacks this beat.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Paladin</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 376, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-paladin\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Ward</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You placed yourself here for exactly this reason.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When a harmful effect would reach an ally, perform a <strong>Faith</strong> check. On success, grant them <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> \u2014 roll a d6 and place it before their <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Dice</span> now.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> The effect is also reduced in scope for the whole <strong>Scene</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Paladin</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 377, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-paladin\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Divine Shield</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Something steps in front of the blow.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When you or an ally takes damage, perform a <strong>Faith</strong> check. On success, the damage is reduced by 1 <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span> \u2014 choose which die is removed.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> The attacker is <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Paladin</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 378, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-paladin\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Condemn</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You don't curse them. You recognize what they are.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Faith</strong> check. On success, condemn a target \u2014 they are <strong>Rattled</strong> and <strong>Exposed</strong>. This condition persists until they atone or the Scene ends.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> All allies gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on their next Strike against this target.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Paladin</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 379, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-paladin\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Condition</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Aura of Courage</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">While in hand: fear finds no purchase here.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">While this card is in hand, you and all nearby allies are immune to <strong>Rattled</strong>. If an ally would be <strong>Rattled</strong>, remove it immediately.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Each protected ally gains <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on their next check.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Paladin</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 380, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Heal</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You reach into the wound and pull something back.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Medicine</strong> check. On success, an ally recovers 1 <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span> \u2014 choose the die and set it to its maximum face value.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Recover 2 <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Dice</span> instead.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 381, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Sacred Flame</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">It doesn't burn. It reveals.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Faith</strong> check. On success, call divine fire down on a target \u2014 they are <strong>Exposed</strong> and take <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> of bonus fire damage.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> They are also <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 382, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Bless</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Not luck. Alignment.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Faith</strong> check. On success, bless up to 3 allies \u2014 each gains <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on their next check this <strong>Scene</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> One ally's <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost</span> becomes <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> for their next 3 checks.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 383, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Turn the Tide</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The moment breaks. You break it first.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When an ally fails a check, perform a <strong>Faith</strong> check. On success, the failure is converted \u2014 treat their roll as a success. Their narration stands; the outcome shifts.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> They also gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on their next check.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 384, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Channel Divinity</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You open yourself and let something larger through.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Faith</strong> check. On success, channel divine energy \u2014 choose one ally in the <strong>Scene</strong>. They recover two lost <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Dice</span> and remove one condition.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Extend the effect to a second ally.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 385, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Fortify</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You shore them up before the next wave comes.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Faith</strong> check. On success, grant <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> to up to two allies \u2014 roll a d6 for each and place it before their <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Dice</span>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Grant <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> to a third ally.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 386, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Word of Ruin</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">One sentence. Their foundation cracks.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Presence</strong> check. On success, speak a devastating truth or condemnation \u2014 the target is <strong>Rattled</strong> and <strong>Exposed</strong> until they recover their composure.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> The condition spreads to one nearby witness.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 387, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Condition</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Spirit Guardians</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">While in hand: the unseen surround you.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">While this card is in hand, any enemy who enters your space is <strong>Rattled</strong> and must succeed on a check to advance further.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> The nearest enemy is also <strong>Rooted</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 388, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Divine Intervention</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You asked. Something answered.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Faith</strong> check at Hard difficulty. On success, name one thing you need \u2014 the divine provides it. The GM narrates how. This cannot be used twice in the same <strong>Scene</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> All allies gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on every check this beat.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 389, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Commune</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You ask. Something answers.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Faith</strong> check. On success:</div><div class=\"co\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"ql\"><div class=\"qi\">What does my deity want me to do here?</div><div class=\"qi\">What truth about this <strong>Scene</strong> am I missing?</div><div class=\"qi\">What is the most righteous path forward?</div></div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Ask one additional question.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 390, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Condition</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Devoted Presence</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">While in hand: your faith is a shield for those around you.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">While this card is in hand, any ally who loses a <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span> within your sight may immediately gain <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> \u2014 roll a d6 and place it before their remaining <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Dice</span>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> You also gain <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> when this triggers.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 391, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Mystic Arcanum</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Beyond the pact. Beyond what was promised.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Arcana</strong> check. On success, channel a power above your tier \u2014 describe an effect of Tier 2 magnitude. The GM adjudicates the cost.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> The cost is waived this time.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 392, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Restoration</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The damage was real. So is this.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Medicine</strong> check. On success, restore up to two lost <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Dice</span> to an ally \u2014 describe how the healing manifests.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Also remove all negative conditions from them.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 393, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Turn</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Your faith is an argument. Some things cannot counter it.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Faith</strong> check. On success, present your holy symbol or conviction \u2014 undead, fiends, or those acting against your deity's domain are repelled and cannot approach until the <strong>Scene</strong> shifts.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> One target flees entirely.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 394, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Eldritch Sight</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You see what was always there.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Arcana</strong> check. On success, perceive all magical auras, hidden enchantments, and true forms in the <strong>Scene</strong> \u2014 gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on any check where this sight is an advantage.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> You also sense a creature's emotional state or intention.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 395, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Mire</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The ground remembers your patron's patience.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Arcana</strong> check. On success, conjure eldritch mire across a zone \u2014 all enemies in it are <strong>Rooted</strong> and must spend an <strong>Action</strong> to break free.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> They are also <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 396, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Shadow Step</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Between here and there, nothing sees you.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Arcana</strong> check. On success, dissolve into shadow \u2014 <strong>Move</strong> to any unoccupied dark space in the <strong>Scene</strong> and become <strong>Hidden</strong> until you act.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on your first <strong>Action</strong> after emerging.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 397, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Condition</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Pact Blade</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">While in hand: the blade knows what it is.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">While this card is in hand, your melee weapon is infused with eldritch force. <strong>Strike</strong> checks gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> and count as magical for purposes of overcoming resistance.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> The target is <strong>Exposed</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 398, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-ranger\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Called Shot</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You weren't aiming at them. You were aiming at something specific.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Precision</strong> check. On success, <strong>Strike</strong> at range \u2014 name the location. The GM applies a matching condition: hands drop things, legs become <strong>Rooted</strong>, voice is silenced.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Condition lasts the full <strong>Scene</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Ranger</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 399, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-ranger\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Set Trap</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You prepared for this before they arrived.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Survival</strong> check. On success, place a trap in any position you can reach \u2014 declare its trigger. When triggered, target is <strong>Rooted</strong> and <strong>Exposed</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> The trap also affects one additional adjacent target.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Ranger</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 400, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-ranger\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Hunter's Eye</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You see the shape of what they're trying to hide.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Perception</strong> check. On success:</div><div class=\"co\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"ql\"><div class=\"qi\">Where is the target most vulnerable right now?</div><div class=\"qi\">What are they trying to conceal about their position?</div><div class=\"qi\">What will they do if pressured?</div></div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Ask one additional question.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Ranger</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 401, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-wizard\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Magic Missile</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">No aim required. That's the point.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Arcana</strong> check. On success, launch three bolts of arcane force \u2014 each deals 1 damage to a target of your choice (can all hit the same target). No roll to hit; each bolt lands automatically.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> One target is also <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Wizard</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 402, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-ranger\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Ghost Step</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Movement with no sound, no shadow, no trace.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Stealth</strong> check. On success, <strong>Move</strong> to any position in the <strong>Scene</strong> without being detected \u2014 arrive <strong>Hidden</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Take one ally with you.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Ranger</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}]